=== RAW MODEL ANSWER ===
Answer: Step 1: Build the activated fused diaza core, e.g. 2-chloro-7-bromopyrazolo[1,5-a]pyrimidine; Step 2: prepare the N-methylpiperidine-substituted pyrazole as a Suzuki partner (pyrazolyl-boronate/boronic acid); Step 3: Suzuki-couple at the bromide to give 7-(pyrazolyl-piperidine)-2-chloropyrazolo[1,5-a]pyrimidine; Step 4: independently obtain enantiopure 3-hydroxy-3-methylazetidin-2-one (free alcohol or protected form); Step 5: deprotonate the alcohol and perform final SNAr/O-arylation at the remaining activated chloro site to furnish C[C@@H](Oc1nc(-c2cnn(C3CCN(C)CC3)c2)cc2nn(C)cc12)[C@H]1CNC(=O)C1.

